ar style="w" strong="H3091">Josué</char> <char style="w" strong="H1961">était</char> <char style="w" strong="H3847">couvert</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H3847">vêtements</char> <char style="w" strong="H6674">sales</char>, <char style="w" strong="H6440">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3091">il</char> <char style="w" strong="H3091">se</char> <char style="w" strong="H5975">tenait</char> <char style="w" strong="H5975">debout</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">devant</char> l’ange. <verse eid="ZEC 3:3" /><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ZEC 3:4" />L’ange, prenant <char style="w" strong="H6440">la</char> <char style="w" strong="H6030">parole</char>, <char style="w" strong="H6030">dit</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">ceux</char> qui <char style="w" strong="H5975">étaient</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">devant</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">lui</char>: Otez-lui <char style="w" strong="H6440">les</char> <char style="w" strong="H3847">vêtements</char> <char style="w" strong="H6674">sales</char>! Puis <char style="w" strong="H5674">il</char> <char style="w" strong="H6030">dit</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">à</char> Josué: <note caller="b" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3.4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">Mi 7:18.</char></note><char style="w" strong="H7200">Vois</char>, <char style="w" strong="H6440">je</char> t’enlève <char style="w" strong="H6440">ton</char> <char style="w" strong="H5771">iniquité</char>, <char style="w" strong="H6030">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">je</char> <char style="w" strong="H6440">te</char> <char style="w" strong="H3847">revêts</char> d’habits <char style="w" strong="H6440">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H4254">fête</char>. <verse eid="ZEC 3:4" /><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ZEC 3:5" />Je dis: Qu’on <char style="w" strong="H7760">mette</char> <char style="w" strong="H5921">sur</char> <char style="w" stro